Package gui

Enum Class ToolbarImage

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ToolbarImage>
gui.ToolbarImage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ToolbarImage>, Constable
enum ToolbarImage extends Enum<ToolbarImage>
An enum listing all available ToolbarImages and defining their name for the file in the IMAGE_ROOT_FOLDER (originally obtained from iconoir.com).
